<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>제보하기</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }


    #title {
        width: 1000px;
        height:40px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border : 1
    }
    #content {
        width: 1000px;
        height: 500px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border:1
    }
</style>
<body>
    <h1>제보하기</h1>
    <p>여러분들의 사연을 전달하여 세상에 알려주세요!</p>
    <form method="post" action="/addIssue">
            <div style="width: 800px;"><textarea id="title" placeholder="제목을 입력하세요." name="topic" style="width: 100%; height: 100%"></textarea></div>
            <div style="width: 800px; height: 500px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: -10px;"><textarea id="content" placeholder="내용을 입력하세요." name="content" style="width: 100%; height: 100%"></textarea></div>
        <select name="type">
            <option value=0>전체</option>
            <option value=1 selected="selected">화이자</option>
            <option value=2>모더나</option>
            <option value=3>얀센</option>
            <option value=4>아스트라제네카</option>
            <option value=5>기타백신</option>
        </select>
        <input type="submit" />
    </form>
</body>
</html>